recorddir="/var/spool/asterisk/monitor/"
find /var/spool/asterisk/monitor -type f -size 44c -delete

for wavfile in `find $recorddir -name \*.wav`; do

wavfilenopath="$(echo $wavfile | sed ‘s/.*\///’)"
mp3file="$(echo $wavfile | sed s/'.wav'/'.mp3'/)"
mp3filenopath="$(echo $mp3file | sed ‘s/.*\///’)"

nice lame -b 16 -m m -q 9-resample "$wavfile" "$mp3file" && rm -frv $wavfile

done

`product_code`  varchar(32) NULL ,

`is_variant`  tinyint NULL DEFAULT 0 ,
`status_event`  varchar(32) NULL ,

`end`  datetime NULL ,
`status`  varchar(32) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'NULL,APPLY,STORE' ,
`create_time`  datetime NULL ,
PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
)
;
